title: Import of skim milk powder in Canada 2020
summary: The graph shows the Import of skim milk in Tonnes Canada during 2020 .
The Import values are in Jannuary .
From February till July the graph oscillate .
gold: A line chart about the import of skim milk powder in Canada in the year 2020 . The year started off with a large plunge in imports , hitting an all time low in March . This slowly grew throughout the middle of the year , finally fluctuating to its all time high at above 350 tonnes and finishing off the year at 250 tonnes .
